<tr>
<td class="mbox-image">
<div style="width: 52px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Edit-copy_purple-wikiq.svg" class="image" title="Copy icon"><img alt="Copy icon" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3e/Edit-copy_purple-wikiq.svg/40px-Edit-copy_purple-wikiq.svg.png" width="40" height="40" border="0" /></a></div>
</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style=""><b>This section is a candidate to be <a href="http://meta.wikimedia.org/wiki/transwiki" class="extiw" title="m:transwiki">copied</a> to <a href="/wiki/Wikiquote" title="Wikiquote">Wikiquote</a> using the <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Transwiki_log" title="Wikipedia:Transwiki log">Transwiki</a> process.</b><br />
