<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="news">"<a href="http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,873557,00.html" class="external text" title="http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,873557,00.html" rel="nofollow">Witness to an Ancient Truth</a>". <i><a href="/wiki/TIME" title="TIME" class="mw-redirect">TIME</a></i>. April 20, 1962<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,873557,00.html" class="external free" title="http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,873557,00.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,873557,00.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Witness+to+an+Ancient+Truth&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BTIME%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=April+20%2C+1962&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.time.com%2Ftime%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F0%2C9171%2C873557%2C00.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Karl_Barth"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
